---

Reference framework: examples/aria/ reconstructs the capabilities of the
shell-based ARIA framework (in this same repository, see archive/aria-shell/
once the runtime ships v0.1) using only runtime primitives. ARIA in turn
draws on patterns from Boris Cherny's subagent architecture and the Ralph
autonomous loop pattern. Both are credited in the architecture documentation.
